HEADWORD: Bacillar
<hw>Ba*cil"lar</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>bacillum</ets> little staff.]</ety> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <sn>1.</sn>
